                <td class="px-6 py-4">✓</td>
              </tr>
            </tbody>
          </table>
        </div>
        {/* FAQ Section */}
        <div class="mb-16">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary mb-6">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
          <div class="space-y-6">
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg text-gray-700 dark:text-white mb-2">What exactly does QualifyMe do?</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">QualifyMe uses AI to automate resume screening, conduct structured interviews (MCQ, coding, and video-based), evaluate candidates, and deliver ranked shortlists—freeing your team from repetitive tasks.</p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg text-gray-700 dark:text-white mb-2">How accurate is the AI evaluation?</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">Our AI evaluates both structured (coding, multiple‑choice) and unstructured (video/text) responses using NLP and scoring algorithms trained to predict real hiring outcomes. While it's not 100% perfect, it's rigorously validated to align with ideal candidate fit.</p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg text-gray-700 dark:text-white mb-2">How does QualifyMe support unbiased hiring?</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">By design, our AI ignores age, gender, ethnicity, and other demographic cues—focusing solely on skills, experience, and performance to ensure fair, objective evaluation.</p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg text-gray-700 dark:text-white mb-2">Can QualifyMe work with my current HR tools?</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">Yes—integrate QualifyMe seamlessly with your existing ATS (e.g. Greenhouse, Zoho Recruit, Lever) or use APIs and webhooks for custom workflows. Enterprise plans include full integration support.</p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg text-gray-700 dark:text-white mb-2">Will AI replace recruiters?</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">No. QualifyMe enhances recruitment efficiency—not replaces humans. Recruiters still make hiring decisions. AI handles initial screening and screening steps so your team can focus on final assessment and cultural fit.</p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg text-gray-700 dark:text-white mb-2">How easy is set‑up and adoption?</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">Extremely user-friendly. Onboard in just a few steps. Our team is available for guidance throughout your trial. No technical setup required for most features.</p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg text-gray-700 dark:text-white mb-2">What about data privacy?</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">We use end-to-end encryption and comply with global standards like GDPR. Candidate data is stored securely and used only for recruitment.</p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg text-gray-700 dark:text-white mb-2">Can I cancel anytime? Will I get a refund?</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">Yes—you can cancel anytime from your account settings or via support. No refunds for partial months or years. Refunds may be considered within 7 days for annual plans or under billing error or downtime situations.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        {/* Plan Recommendation Section */}
        <div class="mb-16 text-center">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary mb-6">Which plan should you choose?</h2>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200 inline-block text-left">
            <li><strong>Just starting out?</strong> Try the <strong>Free plan</strong>—ideal for one job and a lean team.</li>
            <li><strong>Hiring across teams?</strong> The <strong>Basic plan</strong> offers more scale with up to 1,000 applications and 3 recruiters.</li>
            <li><strong>Growing fast or need full branding?</strong> Choose <strong>Premium</strong> for higher volume, unlimited recruiters, and customizable branding.</li>
            <li><strong>Need full control and integration?</strong> Go <strong>Enterprise</strong>—tailored limits, APIs, premium support, and advanced analytics.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="text-center mt-12">
          <a href="/register" class="relative flex h-12 w-full items-center justify-center px-8 before:absolute before:inset-0 before:rounded-full before:bg-primary before:transition before:duration-300 hover:before:scale-105 active:duration-75 active:before:scale-95 sm:w-max mx-auto">
            <span class="relative text-base font-semibold text-white dark:text-dark">Start Your Free Trial</span>
          </a>
          <a href="/contact" class="relative flex h-12 w-full items-center justify-center px-8 mt-4 before:absolute before:inset-0 before:rounded-full before:bg-primary before:transition before:duration-300 hover:before:scale-105 active:duration-75 active:before:scale-95 sm:w-max mx-auto">
            <span class="relative text-base font-semibold text-white dark:text-dark">Book a Demo</span>
          </a>
        </div>
      </Container>
    </section>
  </main>
</Layout> 